title: My Edited Video
description:
This when I was learning to flying in America on the Space Coast. I was conducting my night landings. Close by the shuttle was ready to launch the next day! What a site.
I was flying a Cessna 172FG. Older plane but great fun and did me proud. This was landing at Space Coast regional (KTIX) in Florida just down from Merritt Island.
